Aisling Loftus https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aisling_Loftus 0 Aisling Loftus (born 1 September 1990) is an English actress. Loftus is best known for portraying Agnes Towler on the ITV series Mr Selfridge and Sonya Rostova on the BBC historical period drama series War Peace.
